title: Cryptovoxels parcel acquisition (2)
body:
There is a new Cryptovoxels sale in Vibes island. There is a buy now option for several parcels from 1.5ETH to 0.5ETH. Here are the links for some parcels with "buy now" option (most have been sold - d) option is available only):

SOLD a) 118m² parcel on Vibes, 6557m from the origin, with a 12m build height, floor is at 0m elevation
https://opensea.io/assets/0x79986af15539de2db9a5086382daeda917a9cf0c/4794
SOLD b) 107m² parcel on Vibes, 6631m from the origin, with a 8m build height, floor is at 0m elevation
https://opensea.io/assets/0x79986af15539de2db9a5086382daeda917a9cf0c/4798
SOLD c) 103m² parcel on Vibes, 6602m from the origin, with a 15m build height, floor is at 0m elevation
https://opensea.io/assets/0x79986af15539de2db9a5086382daeda917a9cf0c/4796

d) 62m² parcel on Vibes, 6618m from the origin, with a 10m build height, floor is at 0m elevation
https://opensea.io/assets/0x79986af15539de2db9a5086382daeda917a9cf0c/4797

We can buy that for 1ETH or less.

Furthermore, we can place our bids up to 2.5 ETH for an auction. One of those parcels is next to @Etheopath 's parcel and as he stated we can build something together:
https://discordapp.com/channels/816864150016753705/826530893782581309/844322300672606209
293m² parcel on Vibes, 6516m from the origin, with a 10m build height, floor is at 0m elevation
https://opensea.io/assets/0x79986aF15539de2db9A5086382daEdA917A9CF0C/4833

This parcel is also near to @Etheopath 's but I do not believe we can build together on this one, except we own the other one.
227m² parcel on Vibes, 6525m from the origin, with a 10m build height, floor is at 0m elevation
https://opensea.io/assets/0x79986aF15539de2db9A5086382daEdA917A9CF0C/4822

In this link you can see other listings of similar size parcels which are auctioned:
https://opensea.io/assets/cryptovoxels?search[numericTraits][0][name]=height&search[numericTraits][0][ranges][0][max]=48&search[numericTraits][0][ranges][0][min]=10&search[numericTraits][1][name]=area&search[numericTraits][1][ranges][0][min]=198&search[numericTraits][1][ranges][0][max]=495&search[resultModel]=ASSETS&search[toggles][0]=ON_AUCTION

We will prioritize purchasing a parcel next to Etheopath. None of the current buy it now options are next to his. If we become priced out of bids next to etheopath's, we will aim for the cheapest parcel(s). If we are unable to purchase parcels bordering Etheopath's, then we will focus on purchasing neighboring parcels.

Sale map: https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/826530893782581309/844670305686782012/unknown.png

VOTE OPTIONS (there is a max number of characters, so please check here for full description of each option)

1. Aye, place a bid up to 2.5ETH for one parcel
2. Aye, place bids up to 2.5ETH for two parcels  (or less if the neighboring parcel is smaller)
3. Aye, just buy a parcel for ~ 1 ETH or less.
4. Aye, buy a parcel for ~ 1 ETH or less and place a bid up to 2.5ETH for one parcel
5. Aye, buy a parcel for ~1 ETH or less and place bids up to 2.5ETH each, for two parcels (or less if the neighboring parcel is smaller)
6. Nay, we do not need any parcel in Vibes island.
